name: Black and White Woven Bag
description: This Lovely soft handbag woven in black and white waterproof fabric, with a crystal encrusted front flap which conceals a zip fastening is ideal for adding a little sparkle to your day, wether it be work rest or play!!!

name: Designer Inspired Box Handbag
description: This Designer Inspired Handbag is an absolutely stunning piece.  With plenty of room for all of your must have's...make up, diary, mobile phone etc... and a Patent finish that is encrusted with sparkling crystals, as well as the adjustable chain handles, means that this Timeless piece of 'Arm Candy will last you a lifetime.

name: Geometric Box Clutch Bag
description: This Oyster coloured satin box clutch bag is encased in a silver geometric cage with a sparkling crystal clasp fastening!! Will add the 'Wow' factor to any ensemble!!!

name: Silver Tassle Clutch
description: This Cute Silver Clutch bag will spice up any outfit with ease.  The laced edge detail and long tassle give it that little 'something' that makes this bag stand out from the rest!!! It is also surprisingly roomy too, making it a must have Fashion Accessory!!

name: Gold Tassle Clutch
description: This cute Golden Clutch bag will spice up any outfit with ease.  The laced edge detail and long tassle give it that little 'something' that makes this bag stand out from the rest!!!  It is also surprisingly roomy too, making it a must have Fashion Accessory!!

name: Lace Box Clutch Bag

With rainbow crystals set along the length of its spine and tail, it is also fitted with a hinge which allows the bangle to be worn around the wrist or as high as above the elbow depending on your. preference. This item has the definate WOW factor!!!
